name: Free Clean Queen Mattress
description: Free for pickup. $40 local drop off. It's a bit worn but who isn't these days. Got some light tears, the inner springs are saggier than a new mattress but it hasn't worn a bra since the 70's, so no surprise there. As clean as anything used on Craigslist during a pandemic. I will spritz some disinfectant on it before pickup. I'm only getting rid of it because we downsized to a full. Text or email please. I probably won't answer phone calls.
